 "data": "@startuml
title Policy-Driven Energy Price Shocks & Macroeconomic Transmission

start

:Load Energy + Macro time series via FRED API\n(oil, gas, electricity, CPI, rates, GDP, unemployment, IP);
:Load News via News API / GDELT API\n(policy + economic events, sanctions, shocks);

:Data Cleaning & Processing\n- handle missing values\n- outlier smoothing\n- normalize/scale\n- resample (daily/weekly/monthly)\n- timestamp alignment\n- deduplicate news\n- text cleaning;

fork
 :Time Series Feature Engineering\n- log returns\n- rolling volatility\n- lag features\n- seasonal/trend decomposition\n- technical indicators (RSI/MACD);
fork again
 :News/NLP Feature Extraction\n- sentiment (FinBERT)\n- event intensity score\n- topic modeling (BERTopic/LDA)\n- NER (entities)\n- news volume spike index;
end fork

:Aggregate + Merge by timestamp\nCreate multimodal dataset:\nX_t = [price_features_t, macro_features_t, news_features_t];

:Fusion Layer\n- feature concatenation baseline\n- optional cross-attention/weighting\n- lag alignment (news leads);

fork
 :Time Series Model\nARIMA/SARIMA, VAR/VECM, LSTM/GRU/TCN;
fork again
 :NLP Model\nTransformer embeddings\nPolicy event classifier;
fork again
 :Multimodal Fusion Model\nAttention-based fusion\nHybrid transformer encoder;
end fork

:Prediction Output\n- shock probability (t+7 / t+30)\n- price forecast\n- macro transmission impact (CPI/rates/output)\n- risk index dashboard;

stop
@enduml
